profile:
From home and business repairs to all size of home renovations; bathrooms, decks, interior/exterior trim, paint, flooring and tile ... We handle it all with the same prompt, polite and professional level of service and a very personalized approach.  Call us toll free for a no obligation quote. 
We are licensed, insured, WCB compliant and well versed with building codes / permit requirements.
